ENVWIPE

This little program runs another program with a precise environment.

Symopsis:

$ envwipe [-ims] [-e envfile] progfname {arg0|-} [argn ...]]

where:

-i		add system initialization variables
-m		include standard machine variables (these are dynamic)
-s		include searched variables
-e envfile	include variables from this file
progfname	program executable to execute
arg0		first argument to the program


Standard machine variables include:

SYSNAME
RELEASE
MACHINE
ARCHITECTURE
NODE
DOMAIN

